  "title": "Operator- Production Specialist",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Production Specialist, Manufacturing (4-Day Work Week)</strong></h3><p><strong>Location:</strong> Tuas, Singapore<br /><strong>Schedule:</strong> 4-Day Work Week, Rotating Shifts (Average ~15 workdays/month)</p><ul><li><p>Day Shift: 7:30 AM – 7:30 PM</p></li><li><p>Night Shift: 7:30 PM – 7:30 AM</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Safely operate and oversee state-of-the-art automated production systems.</p></li><li><p>Handle materials, perform tooling changes, and complete routine equipment checks.</p></li><li><p>Inspect finished battery products to ensure top-tier quality standards.</p></li><li><p>Keep clear and accurate production records.</p></li><li><p>Work closely with the team to troubleshoot and improve processes.</p></li></ul><p><p><strong>Monthly Salary:</strong> $2,700 – $3,300 (includes built-in overtime & shift allowances).</p></p><p><p><strong>Shift Allowance:</strong> Up to $15/day (Day) | Up to $25/day (Night).</p></p><p><p><strong>Bonus Package:</strong> 13th-month pay + performance bonus (up to 2 months).</p></p><p><p><strong>Travel Made Easy:</strong> Complimentary shuttle bus from Choa Chu Kang & Joo Koon MRT.</p></p><p><p><strong>Great Meals:</strong> Heavily subsidized at only $2–$3.</p></p><p><p><strong>Fully Equipped:</strong> All PPE provided.</p></p><p><p><strong>Workspace:</strong> Clean, modern, and air-conditioned production floor.</p></p><p><strong>Daily Breaks:</strong> 2 paid tea breaks + a full 1-hour meal break.<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
